dc_title_s: South America, Guyana, Georgetown and approaches (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. "From British Admiralty charts to 1992." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram and tidal information. Inset: Georgetown. Scale 1:15,000. Map no.24388. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
